    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_389486">I loved the early diplomacy quest lines for all the races. It gave a lot of insight into the background and story of the races. Personally, I loved the Dark Elves one the best. I've done crafting, diplomacy, and adventuring. Once I was done w/ the main Raki story line portion of Diplomacy and it went to talking to a few random people.... That kind of blew it for me.<br />
<br />
The one thing that will get me to stay in Vanguard is some sort of good story line aside from Diplomacy.<br />
<br />
<div align="center" style="margin:5px; margin-top:5px; ">
